===Verb===
[[Category:Japanese Type 2 Verbs]]
'''いる''' (iru)

いる is usually written in [[hiragana]].
# to [[be]], [[exist]]
#:'''Usage note:''' いる is only used for animate objects such as people or animals. Inanimate objects use [[ある]] (aru).
# ''(preceded by a て-form verb)'' to be (doing)
